<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 742/98 of 2 April 1998 amending Council Regulation (EEC) No 1101/89 as regards the conditions which apply to the putting into service of new capacity for dry cargo vessels in inland waterway transport </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 742/98, millega muudetakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 siseveetranspordis uue kuivlasti kandev&otilde;ime kasutuselev&otilde;tu suhtes kehtivate tingimuste osas 2. aprill 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1101/89 of 27 April 1989 on structural improvements in inland waterway transport (1), as last amended by Commission Regulation (EC) No 2310/96 (2), and in particular Article 8(1) (c) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. aprilli 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 siseveetranspordi struktuurilise t&otilde;hustamise kohta, viimati muudetud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2310/96, eriti selle artikli 8 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti c, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, for the purpose of calculating the 'old for new' special contribution ratio, it is necessary to differentiate between vessel types on the basis of the three types provided for in Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1102/89 of 27 April 1989 laying down certain measures for implementing Council Regulation (EEC) No 1101/89 on structural improvements in inland waterway transport (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 241/97 (4), with a view to adapting this ratio to the economic realities prevailing in the various sectors of the market pertaining to these types of vessel; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: erilise "vana uue asemel" h&uuml;vitise suhte arvutamiseks on laevad vaja liigitada komisjoni 27. aprilli 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 1102/89 (millega kehtestatakse m&otilde;ningad siseveetranspordi struktuurilist t&otilde;hustamist k&auml;sitleva n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 rakendusmeetmed, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 241/97) s&auml;testatud kolme liiki, et kohandada seda suhet vastavalt seda t&uuml;&uuml;pi laevade turu eri sektorites valitsevatele majandusoludele; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, as a result of developments in the dry cargo vessel sector within the inland waterway transport market, it is necessary to adjust the 'old for new ratio' in order to facilitate the ongoing restructuring of the sector, in particular with regard to container carriers, albeit without thereby cancelling out the effects of the Community scrapping measures of 1996, 1997 and 1998; whereas it is therefore necessary to adjust the ratio for dry cargo vessels by reducing it to 1,25: 1; </inglise>
<eesti> arengute t&otilde;ttu siseveetranspordituru kuivlastilaevade sektoris on vaja "vana uue asemel" suhet kohandada, et lihtsustada sektoris toimuvat &uuml;mberstruktureerimist, eelk&otilde;ige konteinerilaevade suhtes, kuid see ei tohi nullida &uuml;henduse 1996., 1997. ja 1998. aasta lammutamismeetmete m&otilde;ju; seet&otilde;ttu tuleb kuivlastilaevade puhul suhet v&auml;hendada suhteni 1,25: 1; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, the measure provided for under this Regulation has been the subject of consultations with the Member States and the subject of an opinion by the 'Group of Experts on Structural Improvements in Inland Waterway Transport' provided for pursuant to Article 12 of Regulation (EEC) No 1102/89, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetme puhul on peetud n&otilde;u liikmesriikidega ning siseveetranspordi struktuurilise t&otilde;hustamise ekspertide r&uuml;hm on selle kohta esitanud m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1102/89 artiklis 12 s&auml;testatud arvamuse, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The following fourth indent is added to Article 8(1) (a) of Regulation (EEC) No 1101/89: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1101/89 artikli 8 l&otilde;ike 1 punktile a lisatakse j&auml;rgmine, neljas taane: </eesti>
<inglise> '- in the case of dry cargo vessels as provided for in Article 3(1) of Regulation (EEC) No 1102/89, and by way of derogation from the first indent, "one and a half times" shall be replaced by "1,25 times" with effect from 1 April 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> "- m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1102/89 artikli 3 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud kuivlastilaevade puhul ja erandina esimesest taandest asendatakse s&otilde;nad "poolteist korda" s&otilde;nadega "1,25 korda", muudatust kohaldatakse alates 1. aprillist 1998." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the 20th day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub 20. p&auml;eval p&auml;rast Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamist. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 2 April 1998. </inglise>
